---
import LogoShape from "../../../public/Vivrithi_logo.svg";
import LogoShape1 from "../../../public/logowhite.svg";
---

<div class="w-full xl:px-0 md:px-[0px] md:pt-[70px] pt-[40px] px-[10px] md:px-[20px]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 xl:px-4">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between md:gap-30 mb-4 md:mb-20 pt-10 md:pt-0"
    >
      <div class="w-full md:w-2/12">
      <h2
        class="text-[28px] sticky top-0  md:text-[35px] md:text-4xl md:mt-15 font-heading leading-[120%] mb-4 gradient-text"
      >
        Key features
      </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-10/12 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-15 gap-y-5">
        <div class="w-full">
          <img src={LogoShape.src} alt="Vivrithi" class="w-[50px] h-auto" />
          <div class="border-1 border-dashed border-[#F58220] my-6"></div>
          <div class="number_fill text-[14px]">01</div>
          <h3
            class="text-[22px] md:text-[28px] leading-[34px] font-normal mt-4 gradient-text"
          >
            Investor Onboarding
          </h3>
          <div class="mt-2 mb-5 desc text-sm md:text-lg">
            <ul class="pl-4 flex flex-col gap-y-6">
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Commitment Management:</span> Capture investor commitments, fund selection, and legal KYC data.
              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Secure E-signing:</span> Trigger OTP-based e-signing through Leegality for compliance.
              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Lifecycle Tracking:</span> Monitor the full investment journey from commitment to allotment.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full">
          <img src={LogoShape.src} alt="Vivrithi" class="w-[50px] h-auto" />
          <div class="border-1 border-dashed border-[#F58220] my-6"></div>
          <div class="number_fill text-[14px]">02</div>
          <h3
            class="text-[22px] md:text-[28px] leading-[34px] font-normal mt-4 gradient-text"
          >
            Distributor Onboarding
          </h3>
          <div class="mt-2 mb-5 desc text-sm md:text-lg">
            <ul class="pl-4 flex flex-col gap-y-6">
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Distributor Profiling:</span> Record distributor type (RIA, Individual, Organisation) and empanelment details.
              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Hierarchy Management:</span> Support multi-tier structures for large distributor networks.
              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Corporate Mapping:</span> Map team and organisational structures for visibility and control.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full">
          <img src={LogoShape.src} alt="Vivrithi" class="w-[50px] h-auto" />
          <div class="border-1 border-dashed border-[#F58220] my-6"></div>
          <div class="number_fill text-[14px]">03</div>
          <h3
            class="text-[22px] md:text-[28px] leading-[34px] font-normal mt-4 gradient-text"
          >
            e-Sign Integration with Leegality
          </h3>
          <div class="mt-2 mb-5 desc text-sm md:text-lg">
            <ul class="pl-4 flex flex-col gap-y-6">
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">API-Driven Signing:</span> Enable secure OTP-based digital signing via Leegality API.
              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Document Automation:</span> Auto-generate and track e-signed documents seamlessly.

              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Audit Trail:</span> Maintain time-stamped digital records for compliance assurance.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
        </div>

         <div class="w-full">
          <img src={LogoShape.src} alt="Vivrithi" class="w-[50px] h-auto" />
          <div class="border-1 border-dashed border-[#F58220] my-6"></div>
          <div class="number_fill text-[14px]">04</div>
          <h3
            class="text-[22px] md:text-[28px] leading-[34px] font-normal mt-4 gradient-text"
          >
            Distributor Invoicing Tool

          </h3>
          <div class="mt-2 mb-5 desc text-sm md:text-lg">
            <ul class="pl-4 flex flex-col gap-y-6">
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Auto-Invoicing:</span> Generate invoices mapped to fund transactions automatically.

              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Tax and Compliance:</span> Support tax slabs, TDS deductions, and GST compliance.

              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Custom Logic:</span> Fully configurable rules for accuracy and scalability.


              </li>
             
            </ul>
          </div>
          
        </div>


        <div class="w-full">
          <img src={LogoShape.src} alt="Vivrithi" class="w-[50px] h-auto" />
          <div class="border-1 border-dashed border-[#F58220] my-6"></div>
          <div class="number_fill text-[14px]">05</div>
          <h3
            class="text-[22px] md:text-[28px] leading-[34px] font-normal mt-4 gradient-text"
          >
            Brokerage Calculation Engine


          </h3>
          <div class="mt-2 mb-5 desc text-sm md:text-lg">
            <ul class="pl-4 flex flex-col gap-y-6">
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Automated Payouts:</span> Calculate distributor payouts per fund and agreement.


              </li>
              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Flexible Logic:</span> Configure slab-based, contribution-linked, or tenure-based models.

              <li class="list-disc">
                <span class="font-semibold">Real-Time Validation:</span> Integrate with NAV and transaction systems for accurate, up-to-date calculations.



              </li>
             
            </ul>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
